headline: Is Eversource Energy (ES) the Best Dividend Aristocrat Stock with Over 3% Yield?
summary: We recently published a list of the 15 Best Dividend Aristocrat Stocks with Over 3% Yield. Dividend Aristocrats are the companies that have raised their payouts for 25 consecutive years […]
